start: ^Good morning. We begin today with a developing story. Two women were reported missing earlier this week after they were last seen on Sunday night, heading into a wooded area.
news_details_1: ^Those involved in the search say the women were traveling through a remote stretch of forest when they vanished. It’s believed their vehicle may have left the main road sometime after midnight. The surrounding woods are known for complete darkness and no cell service.
news_details_2: ^Search efforts are now focused on deep forest access roads, abandoned clearings, and secluded pull-offs. Poor visibility and rugged terrain are making progress slow. No confirmed sightings have been reported since Sunday night.
news_close: ^Anyone who may have been traveling through the area around that time is urged to come forward. The search remains ongoing. We’ll continue to follow this story as more information becomes available.
